  <FactionDef ParentName="KronostishFactionBase">
    <defName>Kronos_fleet</defName>
    <label>Kronos Fleet Outpost</label>
	<fixedName>Kronos fleet</fixedName>
	<autoFlee>true</autoFlee>
    <description>A fleet of Infinity races that came to our galaxy a long time ago around 5XXX.\n\nThe first ones to encounter them were not found even in records for many years, so I thought they were the first aliens discovered. However, there are people who have human-like appearances and have human knowledge or memories of human days, and there are speculations that they are not ancient humans who went to outer galaxies a long time ago, but they do not know because they do not provide much information. \n\nThese Kronos fleets are just a fleet of the same name, they are different, and even now, a new fleet is coming to the Milky Way.\n\nAt first, they had a friendly relationship. However, by the pirates and those who covet their craft, all but a few fleets have a hostile relationship to this day. But if you like them, you can become friendly.</description>
    <naturalEnemy>true</naturalEnemy>
    <colorSpectrum>
      <li>(1, 1, 1)</li>
      <li>(1, 1, 1)</li>
    </colorSpectrum>
    <maxConfigurableAtWorldCreation>9999</maxConfigurableAtWorldCreation>
    <configurationListOrderPriority>40</configurationListOrderPriority>
  </FactionDef>

